burrow-db (0.2.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Actor-per-Key engine (Erlang-style concurrency)
  * TCP server with binary protocol
  * Async client with connection pooling
  * Deferred persistence (tunable durability)
  * Idle actor cleanup
  * Prometheus-compatible metrics
  * ~34K ops/sec with 100 concurrent clients

 -- BurrowDB Team <team@burrowdb.dev>  Sat, 30 Nov 2024 12:00:00 +0000

burrow-db (0.1.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Core database engine with FlatBuffers serialization
  * Hot-cold tiering with LRU eviction
  * Interactive CLI with verbose mode
  * Full CRUD operations (Create, Read, Update, Delete)
  * Real-time statistics and monitoring
  * Block-based document storage
  * JSON document support
  * Client library for programmatic access
  * Example applications

 -- BurrowDB Team <team@burrowdb.dev>  Sat, 19 Oct 2024 16:00:00 +0000

